So you're the reinforcement from the guild, huh! There's a
really tough guy at the very back! I'm counting on you!
Everyone couldn't wait and got drunk... What should we do?

I'm being forced to drink. If I refuse, it'll be troublesome
later...

Gahahaha!! I can't do my job, so all I can do is drink! I
want to work! I can't work!! All I can do is drink!!

This case... actually, I've invested quite a bit in it... If
it fails... Hya...

I... I don't know anymore... There's nothing... Nothing at
all... that matters...

The monsters are dangerous, and the guys are all beaten
up.... Ah... I wonder if I should have a drink too....

It seems like you can return from here.... Shall we go back
to Ulyssean?

\SE[16] Alright... it's time to work...! \!\SE[15] Let's do
our best today too!!

\SE[72] It's good to have motivation. \SE[7] In that case,
it might be a good idea to be more conscious of
coordination. \SE[7] I think it's better to broaden our
strategic options while we can.

Practice makes perfect. \.Laura.\. You should try deciding
for yourself.

\SE[48]In life, everything is an experience. \!\SE[79]It's
better to go through hardships while you're young.

\SE\SE[0] It's okay. I believe you can do it. \!\SE[0]
Besides, even if by any chance... if we were to be wiped out
due to your command mistake...

give my life for you. \SE[0]So please, feel free to say it
anytime.

things out casually, while experimenting with various
things.

With the four of us, the things we can do have increased.
Let's divide our roles into attack, healing, and support,
and proceed with battles efficiently!

\SE[3] (Because Vega takes the lead and pulls us along, the

making it easier...)
